About
=====

A parser for the Temporal Logic of Actions (TLA+).
[PLY](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/ply/3.4) (Python `lex`-`yacc`) is used to generate the parser.
Classes for a TLA+ abstract tree are included and used for representing the result of parsing.

To install:

```
pip install tla
```
